gmssl
------------------------------------------
Chinese national cryptographic algorithms and protocols

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libgmssl-devel-3.2.0-1bl1
  libgmssl3-3.2.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/guanzhi/GmSSL

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/guanzhi/GmSSL/archive/refs/tags/v3.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gmssl-3.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gmssl-3.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gmssl-3.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gmssl-3.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgmssl3-3.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgmssl-devel-3.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

